KARACHI, Aug 26 (APP):The President Dr. Arif Ali on Saturday visited the mausoleum of father of the nation Quaid-e-Azam Mohammed Ali Jinnah and planted saplings of ‘Mango’ on its premises.
On the occasion, First Lady Samina Alvi was also accompanied by the President.
